          <title>Allen ties playoff career high with 22 points as Cavaliers beat Raptors 114-102 to advance</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Jarrett Allen tied his playoff career high with 22 points and grabbed 19 rebounds as the Cleveland Cavaliers advanced to the Eastern Conference semifinals with a 114-102 victory over the Toronto Raptors.]]></description>
